Subject: [PATCH] customizations: no auto-commit, KISS, subagent type routing

- Remove auto-commit from brainstorming and writing-plans
- Add KISS, reuse, and security guidelines to writing-plans
- Add subagent type selection table for domain-specific agents
- Route implementer subagents to specialized agents (rust-pro, golang-pro, etc.)
- Route Web3 code reviews to git-pr-workflows + security-auditor
